    <briefdescription>
<para>An owning contiguous sequence of JavaScript values. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Copies retain every contained JavaScript value. Moves transfer ownership. Values inserted into the vector must belong to its context; violating this precondition is undefined behavior. Mutating raw data must preserve the same retain/free ownership invariant. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
